  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Overview</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are only some limited resources left in your aircraft, use these resources to escape the enemy's pursuit.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A training system in the aircraft with different levels, challenge the levels to train your control ability and collect coins to upgrade the aircraft.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>After defeat enemy during training/combat, some useful gems/coins will drop. These gems have different uses to help you survive in space, and the coins can be used to upgrade the aircraft.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Different abilities to help defeat powerful enemy</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>How to Use different weapon to defeat enemies</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Different gems drops from enemies help you survive in space</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/2fee1ed38c66936d5892b3a422e9384b.avif?t=1675128424\" width=640 height=212 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect coins to upgrade your abilities to help defeat powerful enemy</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/856181690206e39c8ed1e19d9d974ba8.avif?t=1675128424\" width=640 height=212 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You cannot stop the ship, but you can disable the engine of the aircraft that move slowly and missiles don't trace the ship</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/e4e033715425abd8b1010e92bd0884f0.poster.avif?t=1675128424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/e4e033715425abd8b1010e92bd0884f0.webm?t=1675128424\" type=\"video